thread.title: Michael

author: Michael
title: Michael
text:
I engaged Agent Sean Keogh to sell the family home of 67 years and had full confidence in him from the get go.
Sean's vast experience, professionalism and pleasant manner made for an effective smooth journey. He conducted all inspections and the auction. I was kept informed throughout the campaign and he was very cooperative with any queries.
Sean's enthusiastic and competent approach delivered a pleasing outcome.
